  "title": "Administrative Executive",
  "description": "<p>We’re looking for a full-time to join part of our Family!</p><p>1) Admin Executive</p><ul><li>Invoicing, Taking orders, Purchasing, Data Entry etc..</li><li>Handling of online platform like GrabFood etc (menu update & ordering issues etc)</li><li>Assisting to other Departments if necessary</li><li>ISO recording and documents preparation</li><li>Ad Hoc</li></ul><p>Proficient in Microsoft Window: Excel, Word and Accounting Software: Quickbook</p><p>Location - Kaki Bukit</p><p>Interested candidates, please email us at mingfa.matters@gmail.com</p>",
